    <item>
      <title>自6月以来，印度股票大多数人都会大多数，因为全球增长恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/indian-stocks-slump-most-since-june-as-global-growth-fears-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股票周一暴跌，加入了从东京到悉尼的基准，因为投资者对不断扩大的贸易战争的风险及其对全球经济增长的影响做出了反应]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/indian-stocks-slump-most-since-june-as-global-growth-fears-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 03:59:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将稀土部署为与特朗普的贸易战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-deploys-rare-earths-as-weapon-in-trade-war-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国扩大了关键矿物作为贸易武器的使用，并在稀有地球的出口上有路缘，威胁要改善从电动汽车到武器的高科技制造业中广泛使用的全球关键材料供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/china-deploys-rare-earths-as-weapon-in-trade-war-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 03:39:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自2008年以来，亚洲股票大多数都在全球衰退的担忧中大多数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/asian-stock-benchmarks-drops-most-in-14-years-on-tariff-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲的股票下跌，关键基准在16多年中滑行最多，因为中国股票引起了人们对贸易战对全球经济产生影响的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/asian-stock-benchmarks-drops-most-in-14-years-on-tariff-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 02:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自早期大流行以来，亚洲信用计闪烁最关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/asia-credit-gauge-flashes-most-concern-since-early-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自2020年Covid-19大流行的恶化以来，亚洲的信贷违约掉期损失最大，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对他的全球关税弹a和中国的报复加倍后，风险资产的破坏加剧了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/asia-credit-gauge-flashes-most-concern-since-early-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:57:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战争的增长减缓的恐惧，中国市场卷起了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者为全球两个最大经济体之间螺旋式贸易冲突的影响，中国股票下跌，债券收益率降低了创纪录的低谷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>元贬值市场随着贸易战恶化而增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/yuan-devaluation-market-chatter-gets-louder-as-trade-war-worsens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加深的贸易战正在提高金融市场的猜测，即中国可能会在其追求稳定货币的政策中积极地将人民币贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/yuan-devaluation-market-chatter-gets-louder-as-trade-war-worsens</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 23:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票溃败恶化，债券在关税动荡上集会：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股票的飞行加速了，投资者堆积在避风港资产中，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税加深了中国宣布报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易风险的增加，石油暴跌和沙特削减价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯在两年多以来最多削减了其旗舰原油价格之后，石油沉没了，这场贸易战的不断升级激发了人们对全球衰退和能源需求疲软的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普拒绝市场溃败的恐惧，表明对关税的蔑视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-team-rejects-market-fears-projecting-defiance-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统和他的经济团队驳斥了投资者对通货膨胀和衰退的担忧，对全球关税的市场动荡并没有道歉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-team-rejects-market-fears-projecting-defiance-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 20:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
